  "time_ut": 1657694185,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb9\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Helicopters hovering over the Colombo sky",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Protesters are marching from the President's House towards the Prime Minister's Office. A tear gas attack has been carried out there. In addition, water treatment has also been carried out."
